# graphify-out/ holds a generated knowledge graph, committed on `main` only and
# refreshed by the post-merge hook (feature branches never touch it). Mark the
# artifacts as generated so GitHub collapses them in diffs/PRs; -diff also keeps
# the large graph.json out of local `git diff` noise.
graphify-out/graph.json       -diff linguist-generated
graphify-out/GRAPH_REPORT.md  linguist-generated
